ChecklistItemDescriptionC-35536: Our Fly Well program is a series of wellbeing measures designed to improve safety and help you feel comfortable about flying. Don’t forget your mask! [Learn more](https://www.jetstar.com/au/en/fly-well).
ChecklistItemDescriptionA-35528: There’s important stuff you need to know – start with our [Global travel requirements](https://www.jetstar.com/au/en/travel-requirements-by-destination) page – you’ll find links to helpful resources and information about domestic and international travel requirements for your destination.
